<subSubSection pageId="0" pageNumber="45" type="distribution">
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="45">Distribution and habitat.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="45">
The new species is currently known from Wuhan and Tianmen in Hubei province, China (Fig. 
<figureCitation captionStart="Figure 7" captionStartId="F7" captionText="Figure 7. Distribution of Vitis shizishanensis sp. nov. (triangle)." figureDoi="10.3897/phytokeys.184.70045.figure7" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/604896" pageId="0" pageNumber="45">7</figureCitation>
). It occurs on the scrubland and the roadside of farmland at an altitude of ca. 10-50 m.
</paragraph>
